long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Welkin Health UI/UX improvements for medi.ci Care Team internal use.
Our extension will change phone numbers with label in order to help our employees to have more friendly user experience which has access only to welkincloud that our Care Team uses.
For example the phone number "+1 (000)-000-0000" will be replaced with label that's familiar to our employees like "+1 Medici Gets Medici".
We have a static list of 5 phone numbers that will be replaced with a label accordingly and when a message is received it will make a "ding" sound to notify our Care Team.
